title: DUDES I NEED HELP
body:
I help i buy i new laptop he his a acer with windows 10 and i cant install league why i say errot 1935 when he his installing microsoft visual C++ 2005 redistributale (64x) man help me sorry if you dont understand me im portuguese
{{item:3070}}

replies.body: Grats on your laptop!  It sounds like you may still need to update your windows to the current version, so it downloads necessary assets like Visual C++.  You can also download [Microsoft Visual C++ 2005 Redistributable Package](https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=3387).  That should get you fixed up!

http://esupport.trendmicro.com/solution/en-us/1059423.aspx


https://social.technet.microsoft.com/Forums/en-US/3f465369-269f-4001-a2a7-50cb9b4c613f/error-1935-installing-visual-c-2005-redistributable-x64?forum=win10itprogeneral


http://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/forum/windows_7-windows_programs/microsoft-visual-c-2005-redistributable-error-1935/9b245369-5053-e011-8dfc-68b599b31bf5?auth=1


Try these.  Warning on the 3rd link if you are unfamiliar with editing Registry values,  I would recommend NOT messing with it and contacting a computer specialist to correct the error you are having.

Best of luck.
